<lb n="0021b14" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0021021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】平安時代寫東寺三密藏本</note>清淨觀世<note n="0021022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">音＋（菩薩）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0021022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">音【大】，音菩薩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0021022"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">音菩薩</rdg></app>普賢陀羅尼<note n="0021023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＋（一卷）【甲】</note><note n="0021023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，經一卷【甲】</note><app n="0021023"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">經一卷</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0021b15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0021b16" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0021024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大〕－【明】</note><note n="0021024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0021024"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>唐總持<note n="0021025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔寺〕－【宋】</note><note n="0021025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寺【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0021025"><lem wit="【大】">寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>沙門<note n="0021026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔釋〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0021026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">釋【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0021026"><lem wit="【大】">釋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>智通譯</byline>
<lb n="0021b17" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT20p0021b1701">如是我聞。一時婆伽婆。在王舍城耆闍崛
<lb n="0021b18" ed="T"/><note n="0021027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">山＋（中）【三】</note><note n="0021027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">山【大】，山中【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0021027"><lem wit="【大】">山</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">山中</rdg></app>。與大比丘眾五百人俱。菩薩無央數。爾
<lb n="0021b19" ed="T"/>時觀世音菩薩。與九十二俱<note n="0021028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">胝＝知【甲】</note><note n="0021028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">胝【大】，知【甲】</note><app n="0021028"><lem wit="【大】">胝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">知</rdg></app>菩薩同座。時
<lb n="0021b20" ed="T"/>觀世音菩薩。於晨朝<note n="0021029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（時）＋從【三】</note><note n="0021029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從【大】，時從【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0021029"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">時從</rdg></app>坐而起。整衣服合
<lb n="0021b21" ed="T"/>掌恭敬。頭面禮佛而白佛言。世尊我欲說普
<lb n="0021b22" ed="T"/>賢陀羅尼。為憐愍利益一切眾生故。我從過
<lb n="0021b23" ed="T"/>去月光佛所受得此呪。今欲對佛說此陀羅
<lb n="0021b24" ed="T"/>尼。唯願世尊聽我說之。即說呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0021b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0021b2501" cb:type="dharani">那謨<note n="0021030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔遏〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0021030" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->遏【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0021030"><lem wit="【大】">遏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>羅<note place="inline"><note n="0021031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＋（聲）【明】下同</note><note n="0021031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】下同，上聲【明】下同</note><app n="0021031"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>跢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜耶<note place="inline">一</note><note n="0021032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">那＋（上）夾註【宋】【元】【甲】，（上聲）【明】</note><note n="0021032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">那【大】，那(上)【宋】【元】【甲】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->那上聲【明】</note><app n="0021032"><lem wit="【大】">那</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】">那<note place="inline">上</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">那上聲</rdg></app>謨
<lb n="0021b26" ed="T"/>阿<note n="0021033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利＝𠼝【三】【甲】</note><note n="0021033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利【大】，𠼝【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0021033"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">𠼝</rdg></app>耶婆路枳羝攝皤<note place="inline"><note n="0021034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（上）＋二【宋】【元】【甲】＊，（上聲）＋二【明】＊</note><note n="0021034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】＊，上二【宋】【元】【甲】＊，上聲二【明】＊</note><app n="0021034"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】">上二</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲二</rdg></app>合</note>羅<note place="inline"><note n="0021035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＋（聲）【明】下同</note><note n="0021035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】下同，去聲【明】下同</note><app n="0021035"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>耶<note place="inline">二</note><note n="0021036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">菩＋（去）【宋】【元】，（去聲）【明】</note><note n="0021036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">菩【大】，菩去【宋】【元】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->菩去聲【明】</note><app n="0021036"><lem wit="【大】">菩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">菩去</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">菩去聲</rdg></app>提
<lb n="0021b27" ed="T"/>薩埵<note place="inline">去</note>耶<note place="inline">三</note>摩訶薩<note n="0021037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">埵＋（去）【宋】【元】【甲】，（去聲）【明】</note><note n="0021037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">埵【大】，埵去【宋】【元】【甲】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->埵去聲【明】</note><app n="0021037"><lem wit="【大】">埵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】">埵去</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">埵去聲</rdg></app>耶<note place="inline"><note n="0021038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔去〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0021038" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->去【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0021038"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>四</note>摩訶迦<note place="inline">去</note>嚧儞
